Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.88,0:01:54.09,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.09,0:01:55.55,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,A dream about {\i1}him{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.30,0:02:03.89,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,We're finally here, aren't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.89,0:02:04.77,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.85,0:02:08.60,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,I hope the Master isn't home...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.60,0:02:09.48,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.28,0:02:21.99,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hi...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.99,0:02:23.49,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,It's been a while...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.08,0:02:25.29,Default,Sig,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.29,0:02:26.87,Default,Sig,0000,0000,0000,,You've gotten bigger.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.87,0:02:28.54,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm going to shrink...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.00,0:02:31.50,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Hi... It's me, Alphonse.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.88,0:02:33.38,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,It's been a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.71,0:02:37.97,Default,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,You've {\i1}really{\i0\fscx30} {\r} gotten bigger.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.59,0:02:42.43,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,That's the first time I've been patted on the head since I became like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.30,0:02:46.39,Default,Sig,0000,0000,0000,,Izumi, the Elric runts are here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.77,0:02:48.02,Default,Sig,0000,0000,0000,,Think you can get up?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.39,0:02:49.56,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.56,0:02:51.60,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not feeling too bad today.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.10,0:02:54.31,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,I guess she was lying down because she wasn't feeling well.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.31,0:02:56.61,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Has her body not healed yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.87,0:03:11.25,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,You're one idiot of a disciple!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.25,0:03:13.63,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,What's this I hear about you becoming a dog of the military?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.17,0:03:22.72,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Master! W-Well... about this...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.93,0:03:27.22,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,Al! Look at how much you've grown!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.98,0:03:32.35,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,You haven't changed much either, Mast-
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.32,0:03:37.94,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,You've slacked on your training!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.94,0:03:39.15,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Oww...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.15,0:03:41.45,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you weren't feeling well?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.45,0:03:44.95,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,Forget about that! I'm out of bed like this because I heard you guys were here...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.91,0:03:50.45,Default,Sig,0000,0000,0000,,Don't push yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.21,0:03:54.75,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,You're worried about me, Dear?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.34,0:04:01.59,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know much about the Philosopher's Stone.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.22,0:04:03.84,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,Because I'm not interested.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.84,0:04:05.34,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.26,0:04:10.72,Default,Sig,0000,0000,0000,,We met an alchemist in Central who knew a lot about the stone, didn't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.60,0:04:13.69,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,What was he like?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.02,0:04:16.94,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,I think his name was...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.61,0:04:18.77,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,...Hohenheim.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.37,0:04:30.24,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.33,0:04:32.75,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,So he's alive...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.25,0:04:34.29,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,You know him?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.67,0:04:36.92,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,He's our father.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.25,0:04:39.92,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,So the one who left a long time ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.38,0:04:41.46,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,That bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.84,0:04:46.72,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,It's his fault Mom died.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.26,0:04:48.80,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Because of him...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.18,0:04:57.65,Default,Tri,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! What are you doing up so early?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.61,0:05:01.86,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Al said he needed to pee...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.86,0:05:04.03,Default,Tri,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, so you were taking care of Al.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.03,0:05:05.86,Default,Tri,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Ed.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.97,0:05:33.64,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Mom, where's Dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.69,0:05:38.65,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,He left.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.90,0:05:40.56,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,When's he coming back?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.57,0:05:47.36,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Tickle tickle tickle!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.36,0:05:49.78,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Tickle tickle tickle!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.41,0:05:52.12,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,He'll be back in no time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.74,0:05:54.24,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry and finish your meal, now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.42,0:05:59.75,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Mom...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.63,0:06:03.00,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.92,0:06:06.05,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.47,0:06:14.39,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Mom!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.90,0:06:30.53,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,So... did Dad say anything about the stone?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.11,0:06:35.54,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,He looked happy, saying something about his wish from long ago will finally be coming true soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.71,0:06:39.54,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.54,0:06:41.67,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,Time to eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.25,0:06:43.88,Default,All,0000,0000,0000,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.05,0:06:50.43,Default,Sig,0000,0000,0000,,You aren't going to eat, Al?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.43,0:06:51.93,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,N-No!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.93,0:06:54.30,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,I ate too much on the train...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.30,0:06:58.89,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Hey Al, tell them about how we witnessed childbirth over at Rush Valley!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.89,0:07:00.06,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.06,0:07:03.77,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Master, we helped a baby being born!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.77,0:07:07.44,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot, that doesn't count as "helping".
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.36,0:07:11.99,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,I learned that people are born because everyone in the family works together,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.99,0:07:15.53,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,the mother risks her life, and because the person receives so many blessings from everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.95,0:07:17.04,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.70,0:07:20.29,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,That's how you two were given life, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.29,0:07:22.54,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,Be proud that you were born.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.84,0:07:32.93,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.93,0:07:33.84,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.18,0:07:35.80,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Master hasn't changed at all, has she?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.10,0:07:37.35,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.35,0:07:39.56,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,She hasn't changed at all since we first met her.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.32,0:07:53.16,Default,Man,0000,0000,0000,,Hang in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.16,0:07:54.16,Default,Man2,0000,0000,0000,,Bring over some more!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.16,0:07:55.49,Default,Man3,0000,0000,0000,,It's going to collapse!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.87,0:08:03.67,Default,Man,0000,0000,0000,,The levee's going to break! Run for high ground!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.29,0:08:05.83,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Brother, look!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.01,0:08:11.47,Default,Man,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, it's dangerous!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.33,0:08:40.12,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,This should last for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.45,0:08:43.12,Default,Man,0000,0000,0000,,W-Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.75,0:08:45.79,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,A passing housewife!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.26,0:08:54.26,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Will you please be our master, old lady?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.18,0:09:01.93,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Please, old lady!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.93,0:09:04.98,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't catch exactly what you said...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.39,0:09:07.48,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,Mind repeating it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.52,0:09:10.44,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,C-Correction!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.44,0:09:12.53,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Please be our master, Miss!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.53,0:09:13.44,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.44,0:09:14.61,Default,Both,0000,0000,0000,,Why not?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.61,0:09:16.07,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,I don't take students.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.49,0:09:17.91,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,And besides, we're in the middle of a trip!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.91,0:09:19.74,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Please, accept us as your students!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.74,0:09:21.95,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,God, you're so persistent!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.95,0:09:23.41,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,Do you even have permission from your parents?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.41,0:09:26.29,Default,Man,0000,0000,0000,,The thing is... those boys don't have any parents.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.34,0:09:34.26,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so soft when it comes to things like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.72,0:09:45.31,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,Survive on your own!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.48,0:09:46.48,Default,Both,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.02,0:09:48.35,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,That's the preliminary round.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.85,0:09:50.69,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,If you pass, we'll get to the real training.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.15,0:09:54.48,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,And you're not allowed to use alchemy during this preliminary round.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.86,0:09:55.74,Default,Both,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.32,0:09:58.61,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,"One is All, All is One."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.99,0:10:01.37,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,Find the answer to that within a month.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.12,0:10:06.04,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,If you can't, I'm sending you back to Resembool.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.00,0:10:09.79,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,Later!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.13,0:10:13.92,Default,Both,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.92,0:10:17.22,Default,Both,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.39,0:10:23.76,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,So hungry...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.76,0:10:26.06,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,I want to sleep in a bed, geez...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.15,0:10:36.07,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,What part of this is alchemy training?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.61,0:10:43.45,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,So hungry...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.83,0:10:52.92,Default,Sig,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if those kids are all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.79,0:10:56.46,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,They say there's no substitute for real-life experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.96,0:11:01.64,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,That is the best way to pound the courage portion of alchemy into them.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.22,0:11:07.22,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,If they don't learn anything from this,\Nit just means that's the extent of their talents.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.81,0:11:09.52,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,They'll have to give up learning from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.77,0:11:16.52,Default,Sig,0000,0000,0000,,What I'm worried about is the safety of their lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.73,0:11:22.11,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,I was thrown out to Mt. Briggs in the middle of winter for a month during {\i1}my{\i0} training!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.03,0:11:25.78,Default,Sig,0000,0000,0000,,Don't put yourself and ordinary people at the same level.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.78,0:11:29.79,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,There's so much to eat on that island; they'll live.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.29,0:11:34.67,Default,Both,0000,0000,0000,,We did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.04,0:11:38.17,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,How do we eat this?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.17,0:11:40.55,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm... We cut it apart.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.55,0:11:41.80,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Cut it apart...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.18,0:11:52.35,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.35,0:11:53.81,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,You do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.81,0:11:55.90,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,I did the catching; you do the killing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.90,0:11:58.23,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,You always try to make me do all the things you don't want to do!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.95,0:12:05.95,Default,Both,0000,0000,0000,,Get back here!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.25,0:12:15.79,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Baby foxes...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.50,0:12:22.17,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Forget meat... let's try for some fish.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.09,0:12:28.39,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,How do we catch one?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.39,0:12:31.10,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,We don't have a rod, line, or a needle!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.69,0:12:44.07,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,No food, no fire, no nothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.07,0:12:45.45,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Don't say that!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.36,0:13:22.03,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Geez!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.23,0:13:25.24,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,What was that for, Brother?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.95,0:13:36.16,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.96,0:13:44.26,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Sour!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.39,0:13:52.76,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,I'm... alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.35,0:13:56.18,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Eating ants and living.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.86,0:14:04.90,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Eating life and living.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.28,0:14:08.28,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Living...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.66,0:14:12.99,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,We're not going to die here!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.99,0:14:13.83,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.04,0:14:23.34,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry about this...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.30,0:14:31.51,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,You're almost there, Brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.23,0:14:40.31,Default,Both,0000,0000,0000,,We did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.21,0:15:03.33,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like tomorrow's the end of the month...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.34,0:15:06.00,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Hey Brother,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.00,0:15:09.92,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,did you ever find the answer to "One is All, All is One"?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.09,0:15:16.76,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,I've been thinking about it for the longest time, but I only kind of understand it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.60,0:15:19.52,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not positive, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.14,0:15:24.27,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Remember when I ate ants when we were starving and out of it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.44,0:15:25.90,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,You did?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.90,0:15:27.82,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Yep, I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.82,0:15:29.78,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,They were so sour.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.03,0:15:31.99,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Then, a thought came to my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.45,0:15:34.87,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,If I hadn't eaten them and eventually died,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.87,0:15:36.87,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,foxes and ants would eat me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.49,0:15:39.58,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,I'd return to the soil and become grass.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.04,0:15:41.87,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,And that's what a rabbit would eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.87,0:15:43.67,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,The food chain, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.67,0:15:44.58,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.58,0:15:45.79,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,But that's not all.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.25,0:15:50.59,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Even this island could have been underwater in the ancient times.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.59,0:15:54.80,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,And tens of thousands of years in the future,\Nit could be a summit of a mountain.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.80,0:15:57.35,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Everything is connected?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.81,0:16:02.14,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Everything is within a large stream that can't be seen.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.89,0:16:06.81,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know if that stream should be called the universe or the world,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.44,0:16:12.20,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,but from the point of view of something that big, you and I are like ants.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.03,0:16:15.70,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,A small individual within a stream.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.12,0:16:18.41,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,We're just "one" within the "all".
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.99,0:16:24.67,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,But only when those "ones" gather together, can an "all" exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.30,0:16:32.63,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,It's the promised day.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.63,0:16:36.09,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,Let's hear your answer to "One is All, All is One".
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.51,0:16:38.01,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,"All" is the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.01,0:16:39.60,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,And "One" is me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.44,0:16:46.60,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,Good! We can start the real training now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.69,0:16:49.52,Default,Both,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.65,0:16:55.66,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,A basis of a transmutation circle is the power of the circle.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.66,0:16:58.45,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,The circle displays the circulation of power,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.45,0:17:03.50,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,and by sketching the construction symbol in it,\Nit becomes possible to activate its power.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.92,0:17:12.80,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,This is also a circulation of power.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.47,0:17:16.26,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,It's best to experience it for yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.77,0:17:23.89,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,Now...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.89,0:17:26.73,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,Review it until lunch is ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.86,0:17:30.23,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.23,0:17:32.90,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,The circle displays the circulation of power,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.90,0:17:38.53,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,and by sketching the construction symbol in it,\Nit becomes possible to activate its power.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.70,0:17:43.37,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,But you were transmuting by just slapping your palms together, weren't you, Master?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.91,0:17:48.12,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Do you not need to sketch the construction symbols?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.00,0:17:53.13,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,I am like a construction symbol.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.13,0:17:55.05,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,What do you have to do in order to do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.51,0:18:02.06,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,You might be able to do it if you ever reach the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.69,0:18:10.56,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Master has also seen the truth...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.74,0:18:23.33,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,And? What did you want to talk to me about?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.33,0:18:24.62,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,W-Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.55,0:18:42.10,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,As I thought, you can transmute without a construction symbol!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.14,0:18:46.39,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,Additionally, Alphonse is an empty suit of armor!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.39,0:18:48.89,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,You've got automails for an arm and leg!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.89,0:18:50.52,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,How did you know, Master?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.52,0:18:52.56,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,I can tell from just sparring with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.48,0:18:56.57,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,You... saw it, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.03,0:19:00.20,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,Am I right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.20,0:19:01.49,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes, ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.78,0:19:07.08,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,Both master and pupil, making the same stupid decisions.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.38,0:19:18.55,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Master, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.30,0:19:20.55,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Because you saw that thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.17,0:20:03.93,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,We had a hard time conceiving a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.47,0:20:09.64,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,Just when we thought we were having a baby, I fell ill.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.81,0:20:16.23,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,Because of that, our child wasn't born into this world alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.27,0:20:18.32,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.07,0:20:20.57,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,...I committed taboo.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.61,0:20:25.41,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to that, all sorts of organs were taken from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.24,0:20:28.03,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,I'm such an idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.96,0:20:36.50,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,I should have told you sooner.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.84,0:20:39.96,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,It must have been tough.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.80,0:20:44.88,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,N-No!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.88,0:20:46.47,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,It's something we did to ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.93,0:20:48.97,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,We don't particularly find it tough...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.97,0:20:51.97,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,I think about what to eat when I get my body back.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.97,0:20:54.35,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,It's quite the opposite; it's more of an anticipation!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.27,0:20:57.61,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Right, Brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.61,0:20:58.23,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.23,0:20:59.65,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,That's exactly it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.65,0:21:01.44,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,You morons...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.53,0:21:08.12,Default,Izumi,0000,0000,0000,,No need to force yourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.17,0:21:23.67,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Forgive us...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.80,0:21:25.93,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,We're sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.93,0:21:26.68,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Forgive us...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.14,0:21:28.93,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,We're sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.93,0:21:29.72,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Forgive us...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.76,0:21:31.81,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,We're sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.81,0:21:32.93,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Forgive us...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.56,0:21:42.82,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,This world is flowing while abiding by a great rule that's unimaginable.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.23,0:21:47.07,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Learning about that flow,\Nbreaking it down, and rebuilding it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.70,0:21:49.57,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,That's what alchemy's all about.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.95,0:21:52.62,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,And it's also what living is about, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.58,0:21:57.87,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,The basics of alchemy, breaking\Nsomething down and rebuilding it...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.87,0:22:00.17,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,That's almost like the food chain.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.17,0:22:05.67,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,If you eat a rabbit, you break down\Nits meat and rebuild it into your own body.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.09,0:22:10.59,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,And even that rabbit rebuilds\Nthe grass it ate into its own body.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.39,0:22:15.27,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Alchemy is life itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.87,0:24:01.50,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,A man who enjoys his own desires.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.50,0:24:03.79,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,His name is Greed.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.00,0:24:11.67,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Whether he be friend or foe, the figure that stands before Ed and Al is a body made for fighting.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.47,0:24:16.93,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Next time, Fullmetal Alchemist:
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.93,0:24:20.93,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Episode 13, Beasts of Dublith.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.10,0:24:25.73,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,A powerful figure appears before the two.
